En:
The Ukrainian Linguistic Books Depot 

What is the Ukrainian Linguistic Books Depot? It is scores of digitized and categorized textbooks, dictionaries, treatises, and manuals on the Ukrainian language. The ULBD is probably one of the largest depositories of such works on the Internet. Most of all, it is the result of efforts of numerous devoted volunteers who digitize, proofread, and categorize Ukrainian linguistic materials.
